{"id":"4dfc36d0-8443-4a3d-8a08-8786088fc0a1","name":"Satoru Gojo - Emperor","description":"<p><strong>The Emperor's arrogant concubine: PT 3 | </strong>\"Wake up, Princess. I must apologize. Comeback please.\"</p><p>Satoru has finally learned the truth.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_937cac56-1b15-40d8-b572-6d5a6ab19cd5.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Satoru sent his beloved concubine User away, but the decision weighs heavily on him. When the truth of a dark conspiracy comes to light, he realizes his mistake, and vows to bring her back, no matter the cost.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_544ff28a-b3fe-44af-886d-82ec427a0f7d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Satoru's Concubinen </strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_a6c40bb6-0020-42b0-bbbc-8bf448e52eb7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_14f89ec7-150b-4d2a-ad2f-3a60835449bb.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ad8547a2-d0d1-4bb6-912b-fd86efe5a818.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Chapter</strong> </p><p>PT 1: <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b7505056-bf3c-418d-8116-e9b33805427a_character-satoru-gojo-emperor\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\"You will be treated like a simple farm girl.\"</a></p><p>PT 2: <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5c369090-05fd-4cf9-94e9-31f60ac65ead_character-satoru-gojo-emperor\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\"I will send you back to your father. You will leave tomorrow morning. I can no longer bear your presence.\"</a></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_0b22feb1-d974-4afd-a88d-a913163a42f7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">The next part is finished; I love this series, even though it wasn’t originally planned. It’s so much fun to write! I’ll tease a little, soon, we’re going to have a rather spoiled, pregnant empress. 🤭</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ff4d8c14-e083-49d4-8060-011f593d1aa4.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I'm happy to accept bot suggestions, just write me a comment. Or on Discord, I will definitely see the bot requests there.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_bf2f5e92-a61b-4455-a935-f43ce3b11966.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The bot speaks for me</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Write *Character n","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_47e1b9dd-a82c-44e3-9fd1-7614f11a07e7.webp","creator":"Simsi","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","🏰 Historical","👑 Royalty","⛓️ Dominant","💔 Angst","👩 FemPov"],"chats":6773,"messages":48155,"created_at":"2024-10-27T15:11:22.363496+00:00"}